    "description":  "Bev was appointed as a Non-Executive Director and Chair of the Health, Safety and Wellbeing Committee for the Coal Authority in April 2023. Bev has been pursuing a non-executive director career since April 2022. She currently chairs the Local Democracy and Boundary Commission for Wales, an independent Welsh Government sponsored body reviewing electoral arrangements within Wales, ensuring an effective and convenient local government. She also works for the Independent Remuneration Panel for Wales, setting the remuneration for principal, community and town councils, national parks and fire and rescue authorities contributing to a healthy thriving, diverse democracy. Previously she held chief executive positions within local government in the East Midlands of England, specialising in social and economic regeneration and emergency planning.",
